Frontend MFA UI Cleanup

This plan addresses duplication and logical flow issues in the frontend MFA implementation.

## Objectives
- Eliminate the inline duplicate of the TOTP challenge UI inside `Auth.tsx`.
- Refactor `Auth.tsx` to reuse the `<MFAChallenge />` component directly.
- Remove counterproductive listeners like `usePageData.ts`'s `auth:mfa-required` listener which immediately re-fetches and fails before MFA completes.

## Scope
- `frontend/src/components/auth/Auth.tsx`
- `frontend/src/pages/MFAChallenge.tsx`
- `frontend/src/hooks/usePageData.ts`
